{"tid":1633132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[打氣post] 入黎擺低你想同手足講既說話/ 你曾見證過既人生光輝","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:14:54.000Z","uid":263256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"01b69f534398468569892f3e61771e4cd0e58f46","tid":1633132,"uid":263256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"我要成個post都充滿正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曾經係好早好早期一次 突然地大家需要恐慌性逃難<br />\n我忽然間變成左最後排 廿米後就有癲狗<br />\n呢個時候有位好高既巴打係我面前攝左出黎行去後面擋住 張開雙手叫左句：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地女仔走先！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">多謝你呀巴打！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7dbf4375471c261bd73425245561501691385b2f","tid":1633132,"uid":263256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"屌 P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67e5035d4b23de17fab43da02fc9fbd30e6a56b","tid":1633132,"uid":263256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:56:37.000Z","msg":"我成日都覺得不割席係要兩個人都坐緊係張席上面先有得講<br />\n但明明我地係騎緊膊馬攬埋一舊縛實左 無撚得亦都唔會分開！！！<br />\n我講咁多on9野都係推唔到 P牌 屌！！"},{"pid":"ae8ccde9145560bfbbed9153ae10127ffab02f36","tid":1633132,"uid":263256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}